      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MEPUNGA DESTINY (4) is somehow still a maiden but rarely out of the finish recording six places from eight starts, the latest when sixth at Sandown. Did run very good time (34.94) latest. Tough to beat if on-song. XARA OCTAVE (5) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind Sport Scout (30.75) in a Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Can measure up. HIGH PRAYER (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (26.08) last time in a Maiden at Ballarat. Bold showing expected. YALE DOLLY (1) is new to this circuit but should be in the mix.",
